ActGeneral Campaign Star and General Service Medal Regulations, 2009
SubjectOrder Awarding the General Campaign Star With the SOUTH-WEST ASIA Ribbon
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2010-250 of March 10, 2010; (2) determining the eligibility criteria worthy of recognition by the award of the General Campaign Star with the SOUTH-WEST ASIA ribbon; (3) specifying the appearance of the SOUTH-WEST ASIA ribbon; and (4) establishing the order of precedence of the General Campaign Star with the SOUTH-WEST ASIA ribbon in the Canadian Honours System.
